						<div class="postbody">Messing with other applications running on the same machine, possibly run by other users of the machine in the background or through a network connection, is forbidden.<br /><br />And the classic text mode is such an edge case that modern APIs assume drawing a proportional, usually antialiased font to an all-points-addressable display plane.</div>

